  </mj-head>
  <mj-body width="700px" background-color="#FFFFFF" css-class="mjbody">
    <mj-section background-repeat="no-repeat" padding="20px 0" background-color="#FFFFFF"><mj-column><mj-image padding="10px 25px" padding-top="0px" padding-right="0px" padding-bottom="0px" padding-left="0px" src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0863/8971/9346/files/su38m42y_original.png" alt="hims" width="80px" href="https://links.news.hims.com"></mj-image></mj-column></mj-section><mj-section background-repeat="no-repeat" padding="20px 0" padding-top="40px" padding-right="60px" padding-bottom="0px" padding-left="60px" background-color="#F7F7F7" border-radius="20px 20px 0 0"><mj-column><mj-text align="center" font-family="'Sofia Sans', SofiaPro, Arial, sans-serif" font-size="57px" line-height="1.05" padding="10px 25px" padding-top="0px" padding-right="0px" padding-bottom="16px" padding-left="0px" font-weight="400">Custom care to&nbsp;<span style="color:#d58b6b;">fit</span>&nbsp;<span style="color:#cc8166;">every</span>&nbsp;<span style="color:#a04751;">goal</span></mj-text><mj-text align="center" color="#565656" font-family="'Sofia Sans', SofiaPro, Arial, sans-serif" font-size="24px" line-height="1.4" padding="10px 25px" padding-top="0px" padding-right="0px" padding-bottom="24px" padding-left="0px">Your health history and goals are totally unique—so your care should be too. Discover treatments designed with you in mind.</mj-text></mj-column></mj-section><mj-section background-repeat="no-repeat" padding="20px 0" padding-top="0px" padding-right="60px" padding-bottom="16px" padding-left="60px" background-color="#F7F7F7"><mj-column width="55%"><mj-button background-color="#000000" border="1px solid #AAAAAA" border-radius="100px" color="#FFFFFF" font-family="'Sofia Sans', SofiaPro, Arial, sans-serif" font-size="16px" font-weight="400" line-height="20px" inner-padding="14px 28px 14px 28px" padding="10px 25px" padding-top="0px" padding-right="0px" padding-bottom="20px" padding-left="0px" href="https://links.news.hims.com">Explore all treatments</mj-button></mj-column><mj-column width="45%"><mj-button background-color="#FFFFFF" border="1px solid #AAAAAA" border-radius="100px" color="#000000" font-family="'Sofia Sans', SofiaPro, Arial, sans-serif" font-size="16px" font-weight="400" line-height="20px" inner-padding="14px 28px 14px 28px" padding="10px 25px" padding-top="0px" padding-right="0px" padding-bottom="20px" padding-left="0px" href="https://links.news.hims.com">Learn more</mj-button></mj-column></mj-section><mj-section background-repeat="no-repeat" padding="20px 0" padding-top="0px" padding-bottom="0px" background-color="#F7F7F7"><mj-column><mj-image padding="10px 25px" padding-top="0px" padding-right="60px" padding-bottom="0px" padding-left="60px" src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0863/8971/9346/files/orf3asrh_original.jpg" alt="Hims products" width="580px"></mj-image></mj-column></mj-section><mj-section background-repeat="no-repeat" padding="20px 0" padding-top="48px" padding-right="60px" padding-bottom="0px" padding-left="60px" background-color="#F7F7F7"><mj-column width="55%"><mj-text font-family="'Sofia Sans', SofiaPro, Arial, sans-serif" font-size="29px" line-height="1.15" padding="10px 25px" padding-top="0px" padding-right="0px" padding-bottom="16px" padding-left="0px" font-weight="400">A range of weight loss medications</mj-text><mj-text color="#565656" font-family="'Sofia Sans', SofiaPro, Arial, sans-serif" font-size="18px" line-height="1.4" padding="10px 25px" padding-top="0px" padding-right="0px" padding-bottom="12px" padding-left="0px"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0863/8971/9346/files/fluw48b2_original.png" width="20" height="20" style="vertical-align:middle;margin-right:8px;" />Compounded GLP-1 injections starting at $149/mo</mj-text><mj-text color="#565656" font-family="'Sofia Sans', SofiaPro, Arial, sans-serif" font-size="18px" line-height="1.4" padding="10px 25px" padding-top="0px" padding-right="0px" padding-bottom="16px" padding-left="0px"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0863/8971/9346/files/fluw48b2_original.png" width="20" height="20" style="vertical-align:middle;margin-right:8px;" />Support from providers and ongoing check-ins</mj-text><mj-button align="left" background-color="#000000" border="1px solid #AAAAAA" border-radius="100px" color="#FFFFFF" font-family="'Sofia Sans', SofiaPro, Arial, sans-serif" font-size="17px" font-weight="400" line-height="20px" inner-padding="12px 24px 12px 24px" padding="10px 25px" padding-top="0px" padding-right="0px" padding-bottom="20px" padding-left="0px" href="https://links.news.hims.com">Check it out</mj-button></mj-column><mj-column width="45%"><mj-image padding="10px 25px" padding-top="0px" padding-right="0px" padding-bottom="0px" padding-left="0px" src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0863/8971/9346/files/2lt79jj1_original.jpg" alt="Weight Loss Medications" width="270px" href="https://links.news.hims.com"></mj-image></mj-column></mj-section><mj-section background-repeat="no-repeat" padding="20px 0" padding-top="48px" padding-right="60px" padding-bottom="0px" padding-left="60px" background-color="#F7F7F7"><mj-column width="55%"><mj-text font-family="'Sofia Sans', SofiaPro, Arial, sans-serif" font-size="29px" line-height="1.15" padding="10px 25px" padding-top="0px" padding-right="0px" padding-bottom="16px" padding-left="0px" font-weight="400">Hair Hybrids</mj-text><mj-text color="#565656" font-family="'Sofia Sans', SofiaPro, Arial, sans-serif" font-size="18px" line-height="1.4" padding="10px 25px" padding-top="0px" padding-right="0px" padding-bottom="12px" padding-left="0px"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0863/8971/9346/files/fluw48b2_original.png" width="20" height="20" style="vertical-align:middle;margin-right:8px;" />Regrow hair in 3-6 months or your money back</mj-text><mj-text color="#565656" font-family="'Sofia Sans', SofiaPro, Arial, sans-serif" font-size="18px" line-height="1.4" padding="10px 25px" padding-top="0px" padding-right="0px" padding-bottom="16px" padding-left="0px"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0863/8971/9346/files/fluw48b2_original.png" width="20" height="20" style="vertical-align:middle;margin-right:8px;" />Support overall hair health and thickness</mj-text><mj-button align="left" background-color="#000000" border="1px solid #AAAAAA" border-radius="100px" color="#FFFFFF" font-family="'Sofia Sans', SofiaPro, Arial, sans-serif" font-size="17px" font-weight="400" line-height="20px" inner-padding="12px 24px 12px 24px" padding="10px 25px" padding-top="0px" padding-right="0px" padding-bottom="20px" padding-left="0px" href="https://links.news.hims.com">Check it out</mj-button></mj-column><mj-column width="45%"><mj-image padding="10px 25px" padding-top="0px" padding-right="0px" padding-bottom="0px" padding-left="0px" src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0863/8971/9346/files/p509vyzw_original.jpg" alt="Hair Hybrids" width="270px" href="https://links.news.hims.com"></mj-image></mj-column></mj-section><mj-section background-repeat="no-repeat" padding="20px 0" padding-top="48px" padding-right="60px" padding-bottom="0px" padding-left="60px" background-color="#F7F7F7" border-radius="0 0 20px 20px"><mj-column width="55%"><mj-text font-family="'Sofia Sans', SofiaPro, Arial, sans-serif" font-size="29px" line-height="1.15" padding="10px 25px" padding-top="0px" padding-right="0px" padding-bottom="16px" padding-left="0px" font-weight="400">Sex Rx + Multivitamin</mj-text><mj-text color="#565656" font-family="'Sofia Sans', SofiaPro, Arial, sans-serif" font-size="18px" line-height="1.4" padding="10px 25px" padding-top="0px" padding-right="0px" padding-bottom="12px" padding-left="0px"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0863/8971/9346/files/fluw48b2_original.png" width="20" height="20" style="vertical-align:middle;margin-right:8px;" />Be ready for sex anytime, anywhere</mj-text><mj-text color="#565656" font-family="'Sofia Sans', SofiaPro, Arial, sans-serif" font-size="18px" line-height="1.4" padding="10px 25px" padding-top="0px" padding-right="0px" padding-bottom="16px" padding-left="0px"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0863/8971/9346/files/fluw48b2_original.png" width="20" height="20" style="vertical-align:middle;margin-right:8px;" />Support energy, muscle function, and more</mj-text><mj-button align="left" background-color="#000000" border="1px solid #AAAAAA" border-radius="100px" color="#FFFFFF" font-family="'Sofia Sans', SofiaPro, Arial, sans-serif" font-size="17px" font-weight="400" line-height="20px" inner-padding="12px 24px 12px 24px" padding="10px 25px" padding-top="0px" padding-right="0px" padding-bottom="20px" padding-left="0px" href="https://links.news.hims.com">Check it out</mj-button></mj-column><mj-column width="45%"><mj-image padding="10px 25px" padding-top="0px" padding-right="0px" padding-bottom="0px" padding-left="0px" src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0863/8971/9346/files/zrf1r3i0_original.jpg" alt="Sex Rx + Multivitamin" width="270px" href="https://links.news.hims.com"></mj-image></mj-column></mj-section><mj-section background-repeat="no-repeat" padding="20px 0" padding-top="35px" padding-right="60px" padding-bottom="24px" padding-left="60px" background-color="#F7F7F7"><mj-column><mj-text align="center" font-family="'Sofia Sans', SofiaPro, Arial, sans-serif" font-size="32px" line-height="1.15" padding="10px 25px" padding-top="0px" padding-right="0px" padding-bottom="0px" padding-left="0px" font-weight="400">Take charge of your health with care that puts&nbsp;<span style="color:#bf775d;">you</span>&nbsp;<span style="color:#ac5e54;">first</span></mj-text></mj-column></mj-section><mj-section background-repeat="no-repeat" padding="20px 0" padding-top="30px" padding-right="30px" padding-bottom="16px" padding-left="30px" background-color="#000000"><mj-column><mj-text align="center" color="#FFFFFF" font-family="'Sofia Sans', SofiaPro, Arial, sans-serif" font-size="12px" line-height="1.5" padding="10px 25px" padding-top="0px" padding-right="0px" padding-bottom="24px" padding-left="0px">Compounded drug products are not FDA-approved. FDA does not evaluate compounded drugs for safety, effectiveness, or quality. Prescription products require an online consultation with a healthcare provider who will determine if a prescription is appropriate. See website for full details, important safety information, and restrictions.</mj-text><mj-text align="center" color="#FFFFFF" font-family="'Sofia Sans', SofiaPro, Arial, sans-serif" font-size="24px" line-height="1.3" padding="10px 25px" padding-top="0px" padding-right="0px" padding-bottom="24px" padding-left="0px" font-weight="500">Future you thanks you.</mj-text><mj-social border-radius="0px" font-family="Arial, sans-serif" font-size="0px" icon-size="48px" mode="horizontal" padding="10px 25px" padding-top="0px" padding-right="0px" padding-bottom="24px" padding-left="0px"><mj-social-element font-family="Arial, sans-serif" font-size="0px" padding="4px" padding-top="0px" padding-right="0px" padding-bottom="0px" padding-left="0px" href="https://links.news.hims.com" alt="Facebook" icon-size="48px" icon-height="48px" background-color="#000000" src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0863/8971/9346/files/iv19gvgn_original.png"></mj-social-element><mj-social-element font-family="Arial, sans-serif" font-size="0px" padding="4px" padding-top="0px" padding-right="0px" padding-bottom="0px" padding-left="8px" href="https://links.news.hims.com" alt="Twitter" icon-size="48px" icon-height="48px" background-color="#000000" src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0863/8971/9346/files/nkbu47o4_original.png"></mj-social-element><mj-social-element font-family="Arial, sans-serif" font-size="0px" padding="4px" padding-top="0px" padding-right="0px" padding-bottom="0px" padding-left="8px" href="https://links.news.hims.com" alt="Instagram" icon-size="48px" icon-height="48px" background-color="#000000" src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0863/8971/9346/files/ylx8r55s_original.png"></mj-social-element><mj-social-element font-family="Arial, sans-serif" font-size="0px" padding="4px" padding-top="0px" padding-right="0px" padding-bottom="0px" padding-left="8px" href="https://links.news.hims.com" alt="TikTok" icon-size="48px" icon-height="48px" background-color="#000000" src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0863/8971/9346/files/5as4xrak_original.png"></mj-social-element></mj-social><mj-text align="center" color="#9D9D9D" font-family="'Sofia Sans', SofiaPro, Arial, sans-serif" font-size="10px" line-height="12px" padding="10px 25px" padding-top="0px" padding-right="0px" padding-bottom="8px" padding-left="0px">© 2025 Hims, Inc.</mj-text><mj-text align="center" color="#9D9D9D" font-family="'Sofia Sans', SofiaPro, Arial, sans-serif" font-size="10px" line-height="12px" padding="10px 25px" padding-top="0px" padding-right="0px" padding-bottom="8px" padding-left="0px">2269 Chestnut Street #523 | San Francisco | CA 94123</mj-text><mj-text align="center" color="#9D9D9D" font-family="'Sofia Sans', SofiaPro, Arial, sans-serif" font-size="10px" line-height="12px" padding="10px 25px" padding-top="0px" padding-right="0px" padding-bottom="8px" padding-left="0px">Hims:&nbsp;<span><a href="#">privacy policy</a></span> |&nbsp;<span><a href="#">terms of service</a></span></mj-text><mj-text align="center" color="#9D9D9D" font-family="'Sofia Sans', SofiaPro, Arial, sans-serif" font-size="10px" line-height="12px" padding="10px 25px" padding-top="0px" padding-right="0px" padding-bottom="16px" padding-left="0px"><span><a href="#">unsubscribe</a></span></mj-text></mj-column></mj-section>
